parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description: The exit timestamp of the method call. Unit: milliseconds.

parameters.name: Pid
parameters.description: The process identifier (PID) of the application. For more information about how to obtain the PID, see [Obtain the PID of an application](https://www.alibabacloud.com/help/zh/doc-detail/186100.htm?spm=a2cdw.13409063.0.0.7a72281f0bkTfx#title-imy-7gj-qhr).

parameters.name: RpcID
parameters.description: The ID of the remote procedure call (RPC) mode. You can obtain the ID by calling the **GetTrace** operation.

parameters.name: SpanID
parameters.description: The span ID of the trace. It is displayed on the Trace Explorer page in the ARMS console.

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: The entry timestamp of the method call. Unit: milliseconds.

parameters.name: TraceID
parameters.description: The trace ID. It is displayed on the **Trace Explorer** page in the Application Real-Time Monitoring Service (ARMS) console.
